data.description: Price Improvement! Seller to offer up to $6,000.00 in closing cost if using The Clifton Law Firm. Beautiful corner lot 3 bedroom 2 and a half bath home with a kitchen area that looks over the family den below so no worries about missing out on family time while preparing your family's favorites for the holidays. In the warmer months enjoy sitting out on the quiet front porch enjoying the peaceful qualities of this well kept neighborhood. You do not want to miss this! Schedule your showing today!
